parse.title: List of surface features of Mars imaged by Opportunity

text.*:
Looking north at the southern end of Cape Tribulation (MER-B, 2017)
Newberries at Kirkwood (September 2012)
Fram crater on Sol 84, 24 April 2004

The following is a list of surface features of Mars imaged by the Opportunity rover. Opportunity landed in Meridiani Planum in 2004. (See also Opportunity mission timeline)[1][2][3][4]
